<style>
/* Reset default margins and padding */
body, main {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
}

/* Main content area styles */
.main-content {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  min-height: 100vh;
  width: 100%;
}

/* Carousel container styles */
.carousel-container {
  flex: 1;
  width: 100%;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

/* Carousel item styles */
.carousel-item {
  height: 100vh; /* Makes each carousel item take full viewport height */
  position: relative;
}

/* Carousel image styles */
.carousel-item img {
  object-fit: cover;
  height: 100%;
  width: 100%;
}

/* Centered caption styles */
.carousel-caption {
  position: absolute;
  top: 50%;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  padding: 20px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  max-width: 80%;
  text-align: center;
  color: white;
  overflow: hidden; /* Ensure text does not overflow */
}

/* Adjust heading and paragraph sizes within captions */
.carousel-caption h2 {
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.carousel-caption p {
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  margin-bottom: 0;
}

/* Ensure text does not overflow */
.carousel-caption p {
  overflow-wrap: break-word; /* Break long words */
  word-wrap: break-word; /* Fallback for older browsers */
  white-space: normal; /* Allow text to wrap normally */
}

/* Carousel control styles */
.carousel-control-prev,
.carousel-control-next {
  width: 5%;
  opacity: 0.8;
}

.carousel-indicators {
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
</style>


<main class="main-content">
  <div class="carousel-container">
    <div id="mainCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel" data-bs-interval="10000">
      <!-- Carousel indicators -->
      <div class="carousel-indicators">
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#mainCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#mainCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#mainCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
      </div>

      <!-- Carousel items -->
      <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="carousel-item active">
          <%= image_tag("Slide1.jpg", class: "d-block w-100", alt: "Slide 1") %>
          <div class="carousel-caption">
            <h2>The Garrison</h2>
            <h3><i>"Unyielding Strength, Unmatched Innovation."</i></h3>
            <p>An indigeneous and Private organisation based in India & for India. Committed to safeguard the nation against current as well as emerging threats with deadly force & minimal effort. A new yet bold entry into the Military Industrial Complex of India.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
         <%= image_tag("Slide2.jpg", class: "d-block w-100", alt: "Slide 2") %>
          <div class="carousel-caption">
            <h2>Public Safety</h2>
            <p>We as security company enhances public safety by working closely with individuals and communities. By offering a range of effective tools, this focus on accessible self-defense solutions helps foster a safer environment, enabling individuals to feel more secure in their daily lives.</p>
            
            
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <%= image_tag("Slide3.jpg", class: "d-block w-100", alt: "Slide 3") %>
          <div class="carousel-caption">
            <h2>Military Aspect</h2>
            <p>In addition to our focus on personal safety, we also specialize in military technology, developing advanced tactical gear, surveillance systems, and communication devices for defense organizations. By leveraging cutting-edge innovations and collaborating with military experts, we aim to meet the specific needs of military personnel, enhancing their operational effectiveness and safety in the field.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Carousel controls -->
      <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#mainCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
      </button>
      <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#mainCarousel" data-bs-slide="next">
        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>